content: Two areas are great.  The support is wonderful. ..immediate response and continued follow-up until my problem was resolved.  Second is the app itself. ..wish I had this when I first moved here.
Great app so needed! Every Villager needs it!

I have a Garmin for my car, which of course cannot be used in my golf cart. I can use it in my car, bicycling and walking. It gives you locations of where each golf course, recreation centers, town squares are located. It is totally well worth the money. I wish this app had existed when we first moved here six years ago, it would have saved me many stressful days trying to find my way  around. Even living here now, it gives me locations of places I wasn't even aware they existed in the surrounding areas.
I have never been good with maps so I really love this tool that I can use like a GPS on my cell phone in my GOLF CART or my car. Now I can find everything in The Villages!

Having had the experience of being lost in a golf cart on The Villages golf cart paths only to find my phone's GPS to be of no help whatsoever...... I can assure you, this APP is awesome and much needed! It more than a GPS, it is a comprehensive listing of golf courses, entertainment, town squares, residential villages, restaurants and more that The Villages have to offer. If you live in or around The Villages or plan to visit this APP is a MUST for easy travel in The Villages by golf cart or motor vehicle.

I love this app. I was always getting lost with my regular GPS but this app is amazing and accurate! Whoever created it a genius. Thanks, now I can travel The Villages on my golf cart without having to backtrack.
